<OUTPUT_TEXT>Dear [Customer's Name],

Thank you for reaching out to us regarding your inquiry. We appreciate your patience and cooperation as we investigate your claim. Our team has been diligently working to gather all necessary information and is pleased to inform you that the investigation has been completed.

After careful review, we are pleased to notify you that your claim has been approved for [amount] and will be processed accordingly. We understand that this may be a significant relief to you, and we are committed to ensuring that you receive the compensation you deserve.

Please be advised that we will be making the necessary adjustments to your account, and you can expect to see the credited amount reflected in your next statement. If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to us.

We appreciate your business and look forward to continuing to serve you.

Best regards,
[Your Name]
Senior Customer Service Representative
[Company Name]</OUTPUT_TEXT>
